Ayah?

1077
01:49:08,088 --> 01:49:11,716
Ayah mau kupanggilkan perawat?

1078
01:49:13,593 --> 01:49:16,638
Ayah mau apa? Aku bisa lakukan apa?

1079
01:49:16,805 --> 01:49:18,848
Kuambilkan sesuatu?

1080
01:49:19,933 --> 01:49:21,434
Mau sedikit air?

1081
01:49:24,312 --> 01:49:27,023
Sungai.

1082
01:49:28,608 --> 01:49:30,402
Sungai?

1083
01:49:30,944 --> 01:49:35,073
Ceritakan bagaimana terjadinya.

1084
01:49:36,991 --> 01:49:38,952
Terjadi apa?

1085
01:49:39,953 --> 01:49:42,372
Cara Ayah pergi.

1086
01:49:46,752 --> 01:49:49,255
Yang Ayah lihat di Mata?

1087
01:50:03,268 --> 01:50:06,605
Aku tak tahu kisah itu, Yah.
Ayah tak pernah ceritakan yang itu.

1088
01:50:09,483 --> 01:50:12,528
Baiklah, akan kucoba.

1089
01:50:12,695 --> 01:50:15,280
Ayah harus membantuku.
Katakan bagaimana mulainya.

1090
01:50:17,574 --> 01:50:21,203
Seperti ini.

1091
01:50:21,370 --> 01:50:23,414
Baiklah.

1092
01:50:26,084 --> 01:50:29,504
Okay, jadi sekarang sudah pagi hari...

1093
01:50:29,712 --> 01:50:33,841
...dan kita di rumah sakit,
dan aku tertidur. Lalu aku bangun...

1094
01:50:34,300 --> 01:50:37,637
...dan melihat ayah membaik.

1095
01:50:37,845 --> 01:50:38,972
Ayah?

1096
01:50:39,138 --> 01:50:41,182
Ayah berbeda.

1097
01:50:42,058 --> 01:50:45,061
- Ayah.
- Kita keluar dari sini.

1098
01:50:45,228 --> 01:50:46,479
Dan kubilang:

1099
01:50:46,646 --> 01:50:48,106
Ayah, Kondisi Ayah tak...

1100
01:50:48,272 --> 01:50:50,650
Ambil kursi roda itu.

1101
01:50:53,111 --> 01:50:54,987
Cepat, waktu kita tak banyak!

1102
01:50:55,196 --> 01:50:57,615
Begitu keluar dari lantai ini, kita aman.

1103
01:50:57,782 --> 01:50:59,534
Kita naik kursi roda....

1104
01:50:59,700 --> 01:51:02,996
- Lebih cepat!
...Seolah kita kabur dari rumah sakit.

1105
01:51:03,205 --> 01:51:04,998
Apa yang kamu lakukan?

1106
01:51:05,165 --> 01:51:07,543
Kami melewati Dr. Bennett
yang coba mencegah kami.

1107
01:51:07,709 --> 01:51:10,712
- Keamanan, hentikan mereka!
- Kami melesat di koridor.

1108
01:51:10,879 --> 01:51:12,798
Banyak perawat mengejar kita.

1109
01:51:12,965 --> 01:51:15,008
Ibu dan Josephine di ujung koridor.

1110
01:51:15,175 --> 01:51:17,970
Tak sempat menjelaskan!
Cegah mereka!

1111
01:51:23,642 --> 01:51:25,686
Kita melesat lewati pintu depan
ke trotoar....

1112
01:51:25,852 --> 01:51:30,232
...Mobil tua merah Ayah ada di sana
tapi masih baru..

1113
01:51:30,357 --> 01:51:32,734
Aku mengangkat ayah ....

1114
01:51:32,901 --> 01:51:36,488
...dan Ayah amat ringan.
Tak bisa kujelaskan.

1115
01:51:40,743 --> 01:51:43,538
Tinggalkan, kita tak butuh.!

1116
01:51:45,581 --> 01:51:47,875
Ayah butuh air.

1117
01:51:51,254 --> 01:51:53,255
- Kita ke mana?
- Sungai!

1118
01:52:00,262 --> 01:52:02,723
Kita harus lewat Glenville untuk
hindari kemacetan...

1119
01:52:02,932 --> 01:52:05,684
...karena jemaat gereja keparat menyetir terlalu lambat.

1120
01:52:46,476 --> 01:52:51,689
dan begitu kita sampai ditepi sungai...

1121
01:53:00,366 --> 01:53:02,576
Ia datang!

1122
01:53:02,868 --> 01:53:05,746
...Kita melihat semua orang di sana.

1123
01:53:22,179 --> 01:53:23,764
Maksudku...

1124
01:53:25,015 --> 01:53:26,266
...semua orang.

1125
01:53:38,780 --> 01:53:41,532
Ini sulit dipercaya.

1126
01:53:41,991 --> 01:53:46,204
Kisah hidup Ayah.

1127
01:53:54,754 --> 01:53:57,715
Dan anehnya,
tak satu pun berwajah sedih.

1128
01:53:57,882 --> 01:54:00,426
Semua senang melihat Ayah
...

1129
01:54:01,552 --> 01:54:03,846
...dan mengantar Ayah.

1130
01:54:04,013 --> 01:54:09,645
Selamat tinggal, semua!

1131
01:54:20,989 --> 01:54:23,533
Kekasihku di sungai.

1132
01:55:35,148 --> 01:55:37,942
Ayah menjadi yang seharusnya.

1133
01:55:39,611 --> 01:55:41,946
Ikan yang sangat besar.

1134
01:55:47,035 --> 01:55:49,412
Dan begitulah yang terjadi..

1135
01:55:50,997 --> 01:55:52,791
Yeah.

1136
01:55:55,210 --> 01:55:57,837
tepat sekali.

1137
01:56:39,881 --> 01:56:41,299
Ibu?

1138
01:58:08,512 --> 01:58:11,724
The Lord is my shepherd,
I shall not be in want.

1139
01:58:11,932 --> 01:58:15,436
He makes me to lie down
in green pastures.

1140
01:58:15,644 --> 01:58:18,564
He leads me beside the quiet waters.

1141
01:58:18,731 --> 01:58:20,691
He restores my soul.

1142
01:58:20,858 --> 01:58:24,862
He guides me in the paths of
righteousness for his name's sake.

1143
01:58:25,529 --> 01:58:28,782
Yea, though I walk through
the valley of the shadow of death...

1144
01:58:28,950 --> 01:58:31,578
...I will fear no evil,
for you are with me.

1145
01:58:31,745 --> 01:58:36,041
Pasti kebaikan dan cinta akan mengiringi selama hidupku.

1146
01:59:23,005 --> 01:59:27,509
Pernah dengar lelucon begitu sering
hingga lupa kenapa lucu?

1147
01:59:27,676 --> 01:59:31,764
Tapi kau mendengarnya lagi
dan mendadak serasa baru.

1148
01:59:31,930 --> 01:59:35,058
Kau ingat kenapa dulu menyukainya.

1149
01:59:36,935 --> 01:59:40,105
Jadi katanya ia akan melawan raksasa
yang tingginya 4,5 meter!

1150
01:59:40,272 --> 01:59:43,735
- Mustahil!
- Benar, Yah?

1151
01:59:43,902 --> 01:59:45,195
Begitulah.

1152
01:59:45,361 --> 01:59:47,655
Ya, 'kan? Ia raksasa...

1153
01:59:47,822 --> 01:59:50,283
Kurasa itu lelucon terakhir ayahku.

1154
01:59:50,408 --> 01:59:56,372
Seseorang ceritakan leluconnya
begitu sering hingga dia jadi cerita.

1155
01:59:57,832 --> 02:00:00,168
Mereka terus hidup setelahnya.

1156
02:00:02,420 --> 02:00:05,757
Dan dengan begitu, ia jadi abadi.

